# A Rails Trip Budget App

## Purpose
This is an app that allows a user to set a budget for a trip, track expenses, and view their progress in a similar way to Mint.com.

## Features
1. Create a budget for new trip.
2. Set budgets for default categories.
3. Add expenses to a category.
3. Track the progress by visual graphs.
3. Alerts when you near the budget max.
3. View all trip details.

